<HL>
   Technology:
   Europe Defeats
   Japan's Proposal
   On TV Standard
   ---
   Move Indicates Each Side
   Will Separately Develop
   High-Definition Sets
   ----
   By Bob Davis
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/25/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
